name: Xenolith? Hippodrome?
statement: Input The input contains two integers $$$N$$$, $$$M$$$ ($$$1 \le N \le 1024, 2 \le M \le 16$$$), separated by a single space. Output Output " YES " or " NO ". Examples Input 2 3 Output YES Input 3 2 Output NO Input 33 16 Output YES Input 26 5 Output NO
inputFormat: The input contains two integers $$$N$$$, $$$M$$$ ($$$1 \le N \le 1024, 2 \le M \le 16$$$), separated by a single space.
